{"tid":858324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來洪卓立好後生","createTime":"2018-10-11T17:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T23:51:03.000Z","uid":26761,"like":19,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5b9dc8ee1ffe28fa9f2fc3039c55be3245d3aeab","tid":858324,"uid":26761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:01:17.000Z","msg":"近排見佢出返黎唱歌 好奇之下查下佢幾歲<br />\n原來佢1987年3月2號出世 依家先31歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再睇返佢原來2007年出道 嗰陣先20歲<br />\n之後2008年出咗首彌敦道 相信除咗00後 應該大家都聽過 嗰陣佢先21歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係話有咩特別 但你地諗下自己20歲嗰陣做緊啲咩 可能仲係鳩下鳩下咁hea讀書 但人地就好有理想咁出道做歌手<br />\n<br />\n利申 唔係打手 但最近見佢借youtuber宣傳首歌覺得有啲cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab690e035c35ad712c338a450210d828731be7a","tid":858324,"uid":188733,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/7/76/20091130010248_444cd39872214a8716a8d984d1f39187.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20091214173841\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F7%2F76%2F20091130010248_444cd39872214a8716a8d984d1f39187.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20091214173841&h=a43cc4eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8937c954486e32c3b416e3b4c5329809606dc067","tid":858324,"uid":26761,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2ab690e035c35ad712c338a450210d828731be7a","tid":858324,"uid":188733,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/7/76/20091130010248_444cd39872214a8716a8d984d1f39187.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20091214173841\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F7%2F76%2F200911300102